{
  "stem": "22447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Through Falaise there, where there was a lot of fighting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not with the actual fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the roads.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was up at the front putting up the road signs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when a strange driver comes off from France-- from England, he's going to France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, he's on the wrong side of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] speed regulations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he doesn't know the roads, and you can't rely on the signs, so you have to go buy a map or ask someone where to go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because a lot of them got detached, instead of turning right, they turned left, they got detached from the units.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went on till-- we got to Amiens in September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the Jewish new year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I got the-- the days off, the two days I got off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The timetables, duties were rearranged, so I got those two days off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "While I was there, in Amiens, the message comes through, pack your things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The campaign in Orleans is broken and it's all gone wrong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have to go out there, you've got to get them all out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It all went wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From there we had to go through, so we had to go through-- so right through France, right through Belgium, Brussels.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We stopped at a place called Le Vigne for a few hours, and then we went into Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Through Eindhoven, and then up to, the bridge before Haarlem, there's a bridge, Nijmegen, that was-- at that time-- was the longest-span bridge in Europe-- Nijmegen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a lot of fighting there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had to get them back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The troops, the paratroopers, they carried 48 hours of rations and ammunition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were there for 17 days.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
